rows.label: tlk46320171_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This is the refugee camp distribution
center, but we only distribute rations
during the day. Are you travelers?

rows.label: tlk46320171_01_msg0002
rows.name:
By order of His Holiness Marveni, we provide shelter
and sustenance to the needy.

rows.label: tlk46320171_01_msg0003
rows.name:
However, lately the refugees have
been conducting fierce protests against
the Holy See's Blade policies...

rows.label: tlk46320171_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Many citizens have begun to question
our charity, saying that the refugees
should be made to work for their share.
